          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>Rank:</strong> 417th in the world</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>About:</strong> Esteves is a Brazilian banking magnate and a key figure at BTG Pactual, Latin America’s largest independent investment bank. His expertise in risk management and deal-making has earned him a reputation as one of the sharpest financial minds. Esteves rebuilt his career after facing legal troubles, proving his resilience. Under his leadership, BTG expanded globally, influencing markets far beyond Brazil.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">
          <strong>Need to Know:</strong> Esteves returned to BTG after being cleared of legal charges, making a spectacular comeback. Known as a "finance gladiator," he operates boldly and precisely. His love for soccer often sees him connecting sports with high-stakes business deals.​​</p>
          
